OL,3,CTrainee PC racially abused before
OL,4,Csuicide, dad tells inquest
OL,6,FA trainee police officer suffered
OL,7,Fbullying and racism before his death,
OL,8,Fhis father told an inquest.
OL,10,FAnugrah Abraham, 21, from Bury,
OL,11,FGreater Manchester, feared he would
OL,12,Flose his job and suffered nightmares
OL,13,Fof his station sergeant sitting on his
OL,14,Fchest strangling him, Rochdale
OL,15,FCoroners Court heard.
OL,17,FThe claims, made by his father Amar
OL,18,FAbraham at the hearing, were not
OL,19,Faccepted by West Yorkshire Police, the
OL,20,Fforce's lawyer said.
