OL,3,CTrainee PC racially abused before
OL,4,Csuicide, dad tells inquest
OL,6,FHe was struggling under the pressure
OL,7,Fof working as a trainee PC and also
OL,8,Funiversity work doing a degree
OL,9,Fapprenticeship with the force, the
OL,10,Fcourt heard.
OL,12,FBut his father claimed he was also
OL,13,Fbeing bullied and suffered racism.
OL,15,FHe said his son was born in Delhi, the
OL,16,Fyoungest of three with two older
OL,17,Fsisters, and the family came to live
OL,18,Fin the UK in 2003.
