OL,3,CTrainee PC racially abused before
OL,4,Csuicide, dad tells inquest
OL,6,FHe applied to join the police in
OL,7,FOctober 2021 but problems started
OL,8,Fafter April 2022 when he was posted to
OL,9,FHalifax police station.
OL,11,FWiping away tears, Mr Abraham said:
OL,12,F"He mentioned there is bullying and
OL,13,Fracism culture there, 'My sergeant
OL,14,Fused to bully me a lot, even if I do
OL,15,Fcorrect'. He was completely lost,
OL,16,Freally.
