OL,3,CTrainee PC racially abused before
OL,4,Csuicide, dad tells inquest
OL,6,F"We loved him so much. The last days
OL,7,Fbefore he took his own life he
OL,8,Fmentioned, 'I can't take it, so much
OL,9,Fpressure on me. There's no support
OL,10,Ffrom anywhere'."
OL,12,FSenior Coroner for Manchester North,
OL,13,FJoanne Kearsley, asked Mr Abraham: "Do
OL,14,Fyou think Anu understood how difficult
OL,15,Fit might be working and doing a degree
OL,16,Fat the same time?"
