OL,4,Csuicide, dad tells inquest
OL,6,FMs Kearsley said records showed
OL,7,Fofficers had on occasion told the
OL,8,Fyoung recruit he had done a good job.
OL,10,FAnd GP records showed Mr Abraham
OL,11,Fvisited his doctor in June 2022
OL,12,Fsuffering low moods, stress and
OL,13,Fanxiety, but did not identify any
OL,14,F"triggers" for his feelings.
OL,16,F'I think he was scared'
OL,18,FShortly before his death, the trainee
OL,19,Fofficer was given two weeks' study
OL,20,Fleave and went with friends to
OL,21,FAmsterdam while he was off.
