OL,3,CTrainee PC racially abused before
OL,4,Csuicide, dad tells inquest
OL,6,FBefore he went his sergeant had told
OL,7,Fhim he needed a further development
OL,8,Fand management plan.
OL,10,FBy March 2023 he had been unhappy for
OL,11,Fsix months since being posted to
OL,12,FHalifax, the inquest heard, and he
OL,13,Ftold his father he was suffering
OL,14,Fnightmares.
OL,16,FMr Abraham said: "He felt that his
OL,17,Fsergeant was the weight sitting on his
OL,18,Fchest trying to strangle him. I think
OL,19,Fhe was so scared. I don't know what
OL,20,Fwas going on in the police station."
