OL,6,FHe advised his son to find another job
OL,7,Fbefore leaving the force and on 3
OL,8,FMarch last year, one day before he was
OL,9,Fdue back in work, he spent time
OL,10,Fapplying for jobs then left the family
OL,11,Fhome.
OL,13,FHe was found dead in woodland nearby
OL,14,Fthe next day.
