OL,3,CTrainee PC racially abused before
OL,4,Csuicide, dad tells inquest
OL,6,FHugh Davies, representing West
OL,7,FYorkshire Police, listed the support
OL,8,Fthe young officer had received,
OL,9,Fincluding from his sergeant and
OL,10,Fcolleagues and said the reason he was
OL,11,Fon a development plan was to support
OL,12,Fhim.
OL,14,FHe also had an assessor and a mentor
OL,15,Fand was referred to occupational
OL,16,Fhealth as well as a counsellor.
OL,18,FMr Davies said while in the force his
OL,19,Fdyslexia was spotted for the first
OL,20,Ftime and he received help with that.
